nk\">http://metro.co.uk/2017/10/01/spanish-pm-says-there-was-no-referendum-in-catalonia-after-police-violence-injures-761-6969092/</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Spanish PM Mariano Rajoy has declared that &lsquo;there was no independence referendum in Catalonia today&rsquo;. Rajoy delivered a televised address after violence broke out across the state as Catalonians held what the government called an &lsquo;illegal&rsquo; vote for independence.<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;At this time I can tell you, with full clarity, what you all know and what we have seen today,&rsquo; he said. &lsquo;Today, we have not had a referendum for self-determination in Catalonia. &lsquo;Today, all the Spaniards have seen that our state rule of law keeps its strength and reality, and restricts those who wish to subvert the state of law.&rsquo; Rajoy then praised the Spanish police for responding with &lsquo;firmness and serenity&rsquo; to the referendum.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRead more: <a href=\"http://metro.co.uk/2017/10/01/spanish-pm-says-there-was-no-referendum-in-catalonia-after-police-violence-injures-761-6969092/?ito=cbshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2Fspanish-pm-says-there-was-no-referendum-in-catalonia-after-police-violence-injures-761-6969092%2F%3Fito%3Dcbshare&d=H5S4o0Ff8XTpADkL962R5qEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=a116c5db\" target=\"_blank\">http://metro.co.uk/2017/10/01/spanish-pm-says-there-was-no-referendum-in-catalonia-after-police-violence-injures-761-6969092/?ito=cbshare</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MetroUK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMetroUK&d=H5S4o0Ff8XTpADkL962R5qEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=5c7bc774\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MetroUK</a> | Facebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MetroUK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMetroUK%2F&d=H5S4o0Ff8XTpADkL962R5qEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=d148c0e6\" targ